361
00:34:38,020 --> 00:34:44,650
♫ Setting sail to a far land, but couldn't get over being
perplexed ♫

362
00:34:44,650 --> 00:34:50,200
♫ In coping while in exile, you can't fight against desolation ♫

363
00:34:50,200 --> 00:34:52,140
What type of attitude is that?

364
00:34:52,140 --> 00:34:54,680
I am your savior!

365
00:34:58,860 --> 00:35:03,350
- Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!
- Little Sister!

366
00:35:03,350 --> 00:35:06,520
Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

367
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:14,970
- Little Sister...
- Xiaofeng.

368
00:35:18,270 --> 00:35:21,750
Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

369
00:35:21,750 --> 00:35:23,430
Can you be reasonable?

370
00:35:23,430 --> 00:35:25,370
You cannot even swim! You will drown!

371
00:35:25,370 --> 00:35:27,600
Even if I drown, I do not want to be kissed by you!

372
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:30,740
I don't want to kiss a woman whose heart belongs to another!

373
00:35:30,740 --> 00:35:34,770
I beg you, do not leave me.

374
00:35:36,180 --> 00:35:38,560
I beg of you!

375
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:46,710
My grandfather indeed dislikes the people of the Central Plains,

376
00:35:46,710 --> 00:35:50,430
but he will soon like you like how I do.

377
00:35:57,650 --> 00:36:00,870
- You have not even married. Why are you covering up for him already?
- Drink no more!

378
00:36:00,870 --> 00:36:02,910
Even trying to control her man.

379
00:36:02,910 --> 00:36:06,260
Xiaofeng, will you go anywhere

380
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:08,610
as long as it is with me?

381
00:36:08,610 --> 00:36:12,650
I will go with you. In the future, I will go wherever you go.

382
00:36:12,650 --> 00:36:16,440
Gu Xiaowu...

383
00:36:19,700 --> 00:36:22,230
She is my wife.

384
00:36:24,450 --> 00:36:27,140
No one can take her away!

385
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:33,000
I cannot marry Li Chengyin.

386
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:37,110
I hate him. I hate him!

387
00:36:42,680 --> 00:36:46,730
But she cannot hate.  She must let go.

388
00:36:46,730 --> 00:36:50,180
Only by letting go can she get something

389
00:36:50,180 --> 00:36:53,300
more important in return.

390
00:36:56,540 --> 00:36:59,210
After everything has ended,

391
00:36:59,210 --> 00:37:01,550
he will surely compensate her well.

392
00:37:06,620 --> 00:37:10,870
It's just that I don't know if that friend will wait for him when that time comes.

393
00:37:10,900 --> 00:37:14,120
Turns out...

394
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:18,240
that fox...

395
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:27,080
was not able to wait...

396
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:31,330
for her girl.

397
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:48,620
Xiaofeng... Xiaofeng!

398
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:51,860
Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

399
00:37:56,510 --> 00:38:00,310
Xiaofeng!

400
00:38:03,180 --> 00:38:08,250
Li Chengyin, I forgive you.

401
00:38:08,250 --> 00:38:10,910
I forgive all our happiness,

402
00:38:11,550 --> 00:38:15,570
debts, wild hopes,

403
00:38:15,570 --> 00:38:17,650
and despair.

404
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:26,670
- Your Imperial Highness!
- Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

405
00:38:26,670 --> 00:38:28,640
- Your Imperial Highness!
- Xiaofeng!

406
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:30,170
- Xiaofeng!
- Your Imperial Highness.

407
00:38:30,170 --> 00:38:31,890
- No!
- Your Imperial Highness!

408
00:38:31,890 --> 00:38:38,110
No! Xiaofeng! Come back!

409
00:38:38,110 --> 00:38:42,340
Xiaofeng, you come back!

410
00:39:18,130 --> 00:39:21,610
Greetings to Retired Emperor.

411
00:39:23,720 --> 00:39:27,050
How come you sought me here?

412
00:39:27,050 --> 00:39:32,320
After the abdication ceremony, you disappeared.

413
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,980
Everyone was very anxious.

414
00:39:34,980 --> 00:39:38,500
So I thought that you probably came here,

415
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:40,730
I then came over to check.

416
00:39:42,400 --> 00:39:45,630
The new emperor has ascended the throne.

417
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:48,950
I already gave this prosperous and peaceful country

418
00:39:48,950 --> 00:39:52,270
to the eldest son of Third Royal Brother.

419
00:39:52,270 --> 00:39:55,500
This is the first time

420
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:58,900
that there was a peaceful transfer of the throne here in Li Empire.

421
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:03,840
After all these years, you've been melancholic.

422
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:07,570
Putting all your energy on court matters.

423
00:40:07,570 --> 00:40:10,670
I am worried that once you retire now—

424
00:40:10,670 --> 00:40:15,100
Do not worry. I have more important things to do.

425
00:40:15,100 --> 00:40:18,090
I want to go to Xi State to find her.

426
00:40:18,090 --> 00:40:20,220
Find her?

427
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:27,400
Retired Emperor, Xiaofeng had already left for so many years.

428
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:29,760
You should let go now.

429
00:40:33,710 --> 00:40:38,570
Pei Zhao, you are too gullible.

430
00:40:39,500 --> 00:40:43,730
You actually believed what Xiaofeng wanted you to believe.

431
00:40:46,140 --> 00:40:49,860
Carefully think. She is being angry at me.

432
00:40:49,860 --> 00:40:52,130
Punishing me.

433
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:56,570
She must be hiding somewhere

434
00:40:56,570 --> 00:40:58,410
and living well.

435
00:40:58,410 --> 00:41:01,040
Not wanting to be discovered by me.

436
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:05,410
She just wants to see me anxious and suffering.

437
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:09,810
Your crown princess consort has long been dead.

438
00:41:09,810 --> 00:41:12,650
Her tombstone in Xi State is overflowing with green grass.

439
00:41:12,650 --> 00:41:14,810
She cannot come back.

440
00:41:14,810 --> 00:41:19,210
No! She isn't dead.

441
00:41:19,740 --> 00:41:22,540
How could she be dead?

442
00:41:22,540 --> 00:41:26,460
Pei Zhao, you are too silly!

443
00:41:26,500 --> 00:41:32,200
She is the most brilliant woman in this world.

444
00:41:32,270 --> 00:41:35,370
She must be living well.

445
00:41:35,370 --> 00:41:38,410
